<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q20_v3" title="Q20_v3" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceC</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>En una ciudad viven doscientos cinco mil cuatrocientos treinta habitantes. ¿Cuál de las siguientes expresiones en forma de suma de potencias de 10 representa exactamente esa cantidad de habitantes?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-prompt>¿Cuál de las siguientes expresiones representa correctamente la situación descrita?</qti-prompt>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:msup>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Esta expresión vale 200 000 + 50 000 + 4 000 + 300 + 0 + 0 = 254 300, que no coincide con 205 430.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:msup>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Esta expresión vale 200 000 + 0 + 5 000 + 400 + 0 + 3 = 205 403, que no coincide con 205 430.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:msup>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Esta expresión vale 200 000 + 0 + 5 000 + 400 + 30 + 0 = 205 430, exactamente la cantidad indicada.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:msup>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Esta expresión vale 200 000 + 0 + 5 000 + 0 + 40 + 3 = 205 043, que no coincide con 205 430.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Escribir el número en cifras</strong></p>
            <p>“Doscientos cinco mil cuatrocientos treinta” se escribe:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>205&#160;430</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Sus cifras, de izquierda a derecha, corresponden a centenas de millar, decenas de millar, unidades de millar, centenas, decenas y unidades.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Descomponer según el valor posicional</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>205&#160;430</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:msup>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msup>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msup>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:msup>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:msup>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Verificar la suma numéricamente</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:msup>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>200&#160;000</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msup>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msup>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>5000</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>400</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:msup>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:msup>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>200&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>5000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>400</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>0</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>205&#160;430</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Comparar con las alternativas</strong></p>
            <p>La única alternativa que ubica correctamente cada cifra en su potencia de 10 correspondiente es la alternativa C.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La expresión correcta es:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:msup>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msup>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msup>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:msup>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:msup>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Por lo tanto, la respuesta correcta es la <strong>alternativa C</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>